name: Dare Up Adrenaline
overview: Feel the adrenaline of flying with a wingsuit through narrow passages, dangerous cliffs, and down hills full of trees and rocks that will take your gaming experience to a whole new level! Dare Up! Adrenaline with enhanced graphics and new game play modes. The Wii U version of our most popular and successful title, which already had more than 2 MILLION unique plays on the Web and almost 240 THOUSANDS downloads with its mobile version.
